<br>
I don't ghive a @#%$ about PoP being full of uber content for you Raid types. Seriously, enjoy yourselves and score phat lewts and whatnot. I have never begrudged the uber their uberness.<br>
<br>
My beef is the way advancing to level 65 screws over your gameplay, and the total and utter lack of interesting content for the single-group junky. If you can't see why its so very wrong for a new game expansion to add levels to the list of things that only the Uber should aspire to then eh, enjoy yourself I guess.<br>
<br>
Seems kind of selfish to me though! <p><center>
